# 14 - Learning Plan Creator
# Generate personalized learning paths

NAME learning-planner
INPUT subject
INPUT current_level DEFAULT "beginner"
INPUT time_available DEFAULT "10 hours per week"
INPUT goal_timeline DEFAULT "3 months"

GOAL assess "Define learning scope: $subject at $current_level level, $time_available over $goal_timeline. Output: key topics to cover."
GOAL research "Find 3-5 quality resources (books, courses) for $subject. Use existing knowledge; max 1 web search if needed for current resources."
GOAL structure "Create week-by-week plan with milestones. Keep concise: 1-2 bullets per week."
GOAL output "Format as actionable plan with progress checkboxes. Save to learning-plan-output.md."

RUN plan USING assess, research, structure, output
